RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

94-1979. No. C-940596. State ex rel. McAndrews v. Gaines. Hamilton County,

Reported at 71 Ohio St.3d 1418, 642 N.E.2d 384. It is ordered by the court that the motion for reconsideration in this case be, and the same is hereby, denied, effective December 20, 1994.
